name="Value" value="A part can have one or more alternate parts. The alternate part is interchangeable with the base part in any/all uses."/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{81CB30A2-B2ED-46ef-9284-5C7F3190138E}"/><Extension Object_ID="{7CCD46CE-0E1B-4666-BCFB-4C4DB9E72BBA}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="615"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="165"/><Column name="Property" value="ref"/><Column name="Value" value="PartDefinition"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{A5DCE480-32C8-4d70-A12C-60C1DAA04D9B}"/><Extension Object_ID="{7CCD46CE-0E1B-4666-BCFB-4C4DB9E72BBA}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="632"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="255"/><Column name="Property" value="ref"/><Column name="Value" value="SecurityClass"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{FD902AC6-6E1B-45c1-838C-D851BFCFD939}"/><Extension Object_ID="{6601C16C-8415-4d17-A1B5-34138C4D98E2}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="634"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="277"/><Column name="Property" value="ref"/><Column name="Value" value="PropertyType"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{DD8EE077-0B2C-43f7-A8FA-6D45ADA7AD8F}"/><Extension Object_ID="{F5C78791-E6DB-407e-99A3-838346F3EAB1}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="1964"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="442"/><Column name="Property" value="longDescription"/><Column name="Notes" value="Key features of the UoF applicability statement data model ([referTo/]) are:[randomList]&#xA;[li]It consists of three major components:[randomList]&#xA;[li]the identification and definition of the applicability statement[/li]&#xA;[li]the definition of the evaluation expression (EvaluationCriteria)[/li]&#xA;[li]the identification of the data that is to be asserted[/li][/randomList][/li]&#xA;[li]ApplicabilityStatement does not require an EvaluationCriteria but can contain only a textual expression[/li]&#xA;[li]EvaluationCriteria is always computer interpretable ie, it can be calculated to be TRUE or FALSE[/li]&#xA;[li]EvaluationCriteria must be defined as either:[randomList]&#xA;[li]LogicalAND[/li]&#xA;[li]LogicalOR[/li]&#xA;[li]LogicalXOR[/li]&#xA;[li]LogicalNOT[/li]&#xA;[li]EvaluationByNestedApplicabilityStatement[/li]&#xA;[li]EvaluationByAssertionOfClassInstance[/li]&#xA;[li]EvaluationByAssertionOfSerializedItems[/li]&#xA;[li]EvaluationByAssertionOfCondition[/li][/randomList][/li]&#xA;[li]The value to be asserted can either be an existing value defined by other classes in the data model (EvaluationByAssertionOfClassInstance or EvaluationByAssertionOfSerializedItems) or be an additional condition defined by a ConditionType along with a set of values (ConditionTypeAssertMember)[/li][/randomList]"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{4DC0D750-3448-4a81-B7BB-13DC1F636FEC}"/><Extension Object_ID="{1034E4BE-9AE8-426e-A18D-F5A6431B3801}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="676"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="414"/><Column name="Property" value="ref"/><Column name="Value" value="Contract"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{8619C84F-E2A8-448a-B479-D0DEEC429CBE}"/><Extension Object_ID="{736AFF6C-3DFF-4be4-A2F0-5353213C81FC}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="689"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="498"/><Column name="Property" value="ref"/><Column name="Value" value="Contract"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{0F21A760-4C2C-416e-8F48-998E17642B8D}"/><Extension Object_ID="{D2966483-6CDE-4c2f-9EF8-D9241CE925D2}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="690"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="499"/><Column name="Property" value="ref"/><Column name="Value" value="Contract"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{1EEB5399-E8A6-4cb1-A2D0-0F876DCC360C}"/><Extension Object_ID="{5C041AB0-280F-4271-A90E-E30F39CC3C90}"/></Row><Row><Column name="PropertyID" value="691"/><Column name="Object_ID" value="503"/><Column name="Property" value="example"/><Column name="Value" value="drawing"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{9028B1BE-9829-4857-8B49-B73E9D769475}"/><Extension Object_ID="{1851BB4A-5D77-47f2-B3AA-5013626B94A8}"/></R