when the informationExportTradeControl is set. The agreement should also detail the code(s) to be used for the IEC and exactly which data will be subject to export and trade control.&#xA;Examples of national and/or international regulations are:&#xA;- US regulations on export and customs control (International Traffic in Arms Regulations (ITAR)).&#xA;- German Kriegswaffenkontrollgesetz.&#xA;- Export Administration Regulations (EAR).&#xA;Examples of data subject to export and trade control is the following information for items that are export of trade controlled:&#xA;- hardwarePartTotalLifeLimit&#xA;- hardwarePartOperationalAuthorizedLife&#xA;- partUsageMeanTimeBetweenFailure&#xA;- timeBetweenOverhaul&#xA;- timeBetweenScheduledShopVisits"/><Column name="Derived" value="0"/><Column name="ID" value="1498"/><Column name="Pos" value="7"/><Column name="Length" value="0"/><Column name="Precision" value="0"/><Column name="Scale" value="0"/><Column name="Const" value="0"/><Column name="Style" value="IEC"/><Column name="Classifier" value="33"/><Column name="Type" value="ClassificationType"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{D7A31AA1-655B-4e36-A526-227D7886C71A}"/><Column name="StyleEx" value="IsLiteral=0;volatile=0;"/><Extension Object_ID="{5DC9E75A-3930-4d97-8636-1358E6D672D4}" Classifier="{F0D47512-9495-4c55-AD5A-3AFD91F5BC1E}"/></Row><Row><Column name="Object_ID" value="2033"/><Column name="Name" value="acknowledgementRequired"/><Column name="Scope" value="Public"/><Column name="Stereotype" value="characteristic"/><Column name="Containment" value="Not Specified"/><Column name="IsStatic" value="0"/><Column name="IsCollection" value="0"/><Column name="IsOrdered" value="0"/><Column name="AllowDuplicates" value="0"/><Column name="LowerBound" value="1"/><Column name="UpperBound" value="1"/><Column name="Notes" value="acknowledgementRequired sets if an acknowledgment of receipt is required for the present message."/><Column name="Derived" value="0"/><Column name="ID" value="1500"/