 name="Notes" value="logisticLeadTime indicates the time between the Logistic Support Date for an IPP and start of compilation of an IPPN, taking under consideration the amount of line items, the agreed process of presentation and longest lead time of a spare part within a product.&#xA;&#xA;The use of the logisticLeadTime is to be agreed between the customer and the contractor at the start of the project."/><Column name="Derived" value="0"/><Column name="ID" value="1545"/><Column name="Pos" value="6"/><Column name="Length" value="0"/><Column name="Precision" value="0"/><Column name="Scale" value="0"/><Column name="Const" value="0"/><Column name="Style" value="LLT"/><Column name="Type" value="PropertyType"/><Column name="ea_guid" value="{2A5E533D-47DB-4cc1-B10E-59EEE2D1115F}"/><Column name="StyleEx" value="IsLiteral=0;volatile=0;"/><Extension Object_ID="{DAF7F6C3-70EB-4700-A833-A3C0B918BB72}"/></Row><Row><Column name="Object_ID" value="1961"/><Column name="Name" value="plannedAvailabilityOfObservationDate"/><Column name="Scope" value="Public"/><Column name="Stereotype" value="characteristic"/><Column name="Containment" value="Not Specified"/><Column name="IsStatic" value="0"/><Column name="IsCollection" value="0"/><Column name="IsOrdered" value="0"/><Column name="AllowDuplicates" value="0"/><Column name="LowerBound" value="0"/><Column name="UpperBound" value="1"/><Column name="Notes" value="plannedAvailabilityOfObservationDate indicates the planned date when the observations from customers have to be available for correction of Master Provisioning Data or, in case of extended process, for preparation of PreAssessment Meeting in the planned timescale."/><Column name="Derived" value="0"/><Column name="ID" value="1546"/><Column name="Pos" value="7"/><Column name="Length" value="0"/><Column name="Precision" value="0"/><Column name="Scale" value="0"/><Column name="Const" value="0"/><Column name="Style" value="DOP"/><Column name="Type" value="DateType"/><Column name="ea_gu